FT  18 AUG 94 / International Company News: Colgate buys unit from
Ciba-Geigy
The Indian unit of Colgate-Palmolive said it had signed an agreement to buy
the oral hygiene business of Hindustan Ciba-Geigy for Rs1.31bn (Dollars
42m), Reuter reports from Bombay.
Hindustan Ciba-Geigy is 40 per cent owned by Ciba-Geigy of Switzerland.
